      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Un turratj mannus Likkumus/ un darrajt tohs/ Es efinutas KUNGS/ kas juhs fwehti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Ja jeb fas fawam Tehwam/ jeb fawai Mahtei lahd/tam buhs nokautam tapt/wiꞥſch irr fawam Tehwam jeb fawet Mahtei lahdejs/ winna Affins lai us to paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Un kad kahds Wihrs ar Zit-ta Seewu to Faulibu pahrkahpi/ tam buhs nokautam tapt/ tapehz ka wiꞥſch ar fawa Tuwaka Seewu to Faulibu irr pahrkahpis/ tik labbi tas Pahrkahpejs ka ta Pahrkahpeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un tas Wihrs/ kas pee fa-wa Tehwa Seewas gull/ tas at-feds fawa Tehwa Kaununu/ teem abbeem buhs nokanteem tapt/ lai winnu Affins us teem paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Ir kursh Wihrs pee fa-was Weddekles gull/ teem ab-beem buhs nokanteem tapt/ tee darra weenu negantu Sajaṅk-fchann/ laid winnu Affins us teem paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Ja arridsan Wihrs pee Wihra gull/ itt ka pee Seewas/ tee abbi irr weenu Negantibu darrijschi/ abbeem buhs nokanteem tapt/ laid winnu Affins us teem paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Un kursh Wihrs weenu Seewu un winnas Mahti nem/ ta irr weena neganta Leeta/ wiꞥſch nu lihds ar winnahm buhs ar Ug-guni fadedsnaht/ ka nekahda Blehdiba juhsu Starpâ effoti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Un ja kahds Wihrs pee kahda Lohpa gull/ tam buhs nokautam tapt/ un jums buhs arri to Lohpu nokaut.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Ta patt arridsan/ja twee-na Seewa pee jebkahda Lohpanahk ar winnu fajaufdamees/ tad buhs jums to Seewu un to Lohpu nokaut/ teem buhs nokaut-teem tapt/ laid winnu Affins us teem paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un ja kahds Wihrs fawu Mahfu nemin/ fawa Tehwa Meitu/ jeb fawas Mahtes Met-tu/ un tas winnas Kaununu luhko/ un ta winna Kaununu luhko/ ta irr weena beskauniga Leeta/ tapehz buhs teem no fawu Lauschn Behrnu Azzim isdelde-tam tapt/ wiꞥſch irr fawas Mah-fas Kaununu atfedsis/ tam buhs fawu Noseegutnu nest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Uu ja weens Wihrs pee kahdas Seewas gull/ kurrai us Drahnahyt irr/ un atfeds wiꞥſ-chas Kaununu/ un atdarra wiꞥſ-chas Awotu/ un fcht patti fawu Affins Awotu atfeds/ tad buhs teem abbeem isdelteem tapt no fa-weenim Laudim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Tawas Mahtes Mahfas/ un tawa Tehwa Mahfas Kaununu tew ne buhs atfegt/ jo tahds irr fawu Affins Radneezi atfe-dsis/ teem buhs fawu Noseegu-mu nest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Ja arri weens Wihrs pee fawa Tehwa Brahta Seewas gull/ tas irr fawa Tehwa Brahta Kaununu atfedsis/ teem buhs\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
